Paper: hep-th/0105150

Date: 2001-05-16

Title: A simple proof that $C^{\infty}({\bf R}^n,U(1))$ does not have a Haar

measureAuthors: Wei-Min Sun, Xiang-Song Chen and Fan Wang

Comments: Revtex, 2 pages

We give a simple proof that there does not exist a Haar measure on the group$C^{\infty}({\bf R}^n,U(1))$.